name: Sexy Astronaut Suit
description:
Get early access to build and test build, be able to try all epochs and test them by yourself on Patreon or contact me for support on Discord

Training settings:

85 images, 15 steps, 10 epochs, you find many epochs (with test images using plot xy script) on my Patreon while supporting me.


Recommended settings:

  • Make sure you are aware on the usage instructions of LORA

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras (Recommended for best quality, you may try other samplers)

  • CFG Scale : 5 to 9

  • LORA weight for txt2img: reccomended 0.4-0.8

  • Keys: wearing sexy astrosuit, wearing sexy astrosuit with helmet, mars background, inside space station

I advice to start the prompt with something like "a woman wearing sexy astrosuit with helmet".

Also if you want a mars background i advice to give a weight to mars background keyword, like 1.2 should be enough, if necessary try to use also words like sand and desert.

If you'd like to support my efforts and have access to early and bleeding edge builds, please think about joining my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/betterCuteAsians
